Parser.ElemParsers

Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • Parser.ElemParsers.Parser

  • public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object

    Parser class for parsing data

    Parser class is responsible for all parsing of data from received TCP/UDP hex data to readable format.
